Developers

If you already have a contribution in mind you can find the project repositories on GitHub. For a separate list of projects see here.

We're happy to accept either pull requests on GitHub or patches sent under a pseudonym through Freenet forums such as FMS.

Feel free to join us on IRC: #freenet on chat.freenode.net
